<h2>internet consulting</h2>
    </div>

             <div id="col1" >

The Internet is providing the most powerful information sharing tool in human
history. The most successful companies and organisations will be those that
have the best approach to manage this tool and the information it can provide.

<br /> <br />
<ul>
<li> Are you still relying simply on your search engine listing?		
<li> Can you show the world how you actively manage information?		
<li> Do you have a strategy for seeking new relationships that will match the next market opportunity?
<li> What are the new Internet trends and developments that will impact on your organisation?
</ul>

Our extensive experience with Internet technology, trends, social and economic
environment can help your organisation to position itself properly in this
central area of the information economy.

